<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Reset some default browser styles */
        body, h1, p, a, button {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa, #c3cfe2);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .about-me {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: calc(100vh - 100px);
            padding: 20px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .about-me-content {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .about-me h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .about-me p {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: #3498db;
            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .back-button:hover {
            background: #2980b9;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #fff;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .footer-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .footer-link {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .footer-link:hover {
            color: #3498db;
        }

        .footer-link i {
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        /* Media Queries for responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-me-content {
                padding: 15px;
            }

            .about-me h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }

            .about-me p {
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }

            .back-button {
                font-size: 0.9em;
                padding: 8px 16px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .about-me h1 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }

            .about-me p {
                font-size: 0.8em;
            }

            .back-button {
                font-size: 0.8em;
                padding: 6px 12px;
            }

            .footer-content {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-me">
        <div class="about-me-content">
            <h1>About Me</h1>
            <p>My name is Mohammed, I am a software engineer, I am trying to develop myself in back-end  and cyber security, I always try to create something that benefits those around me.</p>
            
            <div class="button-group">
                <a href="/" class="back-button"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mo-310" target="_blank" class="footer-link"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            <a href="https://github.com/zl1_310" target="_blank" class="footer-link"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
